## 8. TIME ESTIMATION GUARDRAILS

**MINIMUM:** 60 minutes (no issue less than this)
**MAXIMUM:** 120 minutes (no issue more than this)

**SCALING RULES:**

| Issue Type | Time Range | Rationale |
|------------|------------|-----------|
| Static UI pages (no logic) | 60-75 minutes | Simple HTML/CSS/JSX |
| UI forms with state | 65-80 minutes | State management complexity |
| Firebase setup/integration | 70-90 minutes | Configuration + SDK setup |
| CRUD API endpoint | 60-80 minutes | Standard FastAPI patterns |
| Frontend-API integration | 60-75 minutes | Fetch + display logic |
| LangChain/LLM feature | 90-120 minutes | AI integration complexity |
| Multi-component feature | 100-120 minutes | Multiple moving parts |
| Combined frontend+backend | 90-120 minutes | Full-stack feature |

**IF TIME < 60 OR TIME > 120 → ADJUST TO FIT BOUNDS**

